{"title":"树状数组模板","uid":"b5394bf4622b0e5f2930e3e8011548af","slug":"树状数组模板","date":"2022-04-28T13:07:35.000Z","updated":"2022-04-28T13:25:27.130Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/树状数组模板.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"树状数组模板\"><a href=\"#树状数组模板\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"树状数组模板\"></a>树状数组模板</h1><p><strong>代码如下~</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">int lowbit(int a)\n&#x2F;&#x2F;玄学的运算\n&#123;\n\treturn a &amp; (-a);\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;公式记住\n&#125;\nvoid add(int k, vector&lt;int&gt; &amp;tr, int i)\n&#x2F;&#x2F;单点增加\n&#123;\n\tint n &#x3D; tr.size();\n\tfor(int p &#x3D; i; p &lt;&#x3D; n; p +&#x3D; lowbit(p))\n\t\ttr[p] +&#x3D; k;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;每次到左上层，加入k\n\treturn;\n&#125;\nint ask(int i, vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; tr)\n&#x2F;&#x2F;求前缀和\n&#123;\n\tint ans &#x3D; 0;\n\tfor(int p &#x3D; i; p; p -&#x3D; lowbit(p))\n\t\tans +&#x3D; tr[p];\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;每次到左下层\n\treturn ans;\n&#125;\nint find(int l, int r, vector&lt;int&gt; &amp;tr)\n&#x2F;&#x2F;求区间和\n&#123;\n\treturn ask(r, tr) - ask(l - 1, tr);\n&#125;\nvoid build(vector&lt;int&gt; &amp;tr, vector&lt;int&gt; a)\n&#x2F;&#x2F;建树\n&#123;\n\tint n &#x3D; a.size();\n\ttr.resize(5 * n, 0);\n\tfor(int i &#x3D; 1; i &lt;&#x3D; n; i++)\n\t\tadd(a[i], tr, i);\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<p><em>未完待续。。。</em></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"树状数组模板代码如下~ int lowbit(int a) &#x2F;&#x2F;玄学的运算 &#123; return a &amp; (-a); &#x2F;&#x2F;公式记住 &#125; void add(int k, vector&lt;int&gt; &amp;t...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":842,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Code","slug":"Code","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Code.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A0%91%E7%8A%B6%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">树状数组模板</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"YingHN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2